params._buyNowPrice: The price for immediate purchase (set to 0 to disable).
params._minPrice: The starting price for the auction.
params.tokenId: The ID of the token to list.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

placeBid(uint256).notice: Places a bid on a listed NFT. Extends the auction on each new bid.

settleAuction(uint256).notice: Settles the auction after it has ended. Can be called by anyone.

takeHighestBid(uint256).notice: Allows the seller to accept the current highest bid before the auction ends.

unlistNFT(uint256).notice: Allows the seller to unlist an NFT if no bids have been made.

withdrawAllFailedCredits(address).notice: Allows users to withdraw funds that failed to be transferred directly.
